==Compléments==
===Lectures approfondies===
* {{en}} C. W. Murray et H. J. B. Birks - ''The Botanist in Skye and Adjacent Islands: An Annotated Check-list of the Vascular Plants of the Islands of Skye, Raasay, Rona, Rum, Eigg, Muck, Canna, Scarpay and Soay'', 2005 {{ISBN|0954897102}}.
* {{en}} Richard Sharpe - ''Raasay A Study In Island History'', Grant et Cutler, London, 1977/1982 {{ISBN|0729301303}}.
* {{en}} Richard Sharpe - ''Raasay A Study In Island History Documents And Sources'', Grant et Cutler, London, 1978, {{ISBN|0729300609}}.
* {{en}} Laurence et Pamela Draper - ''The Raasay Iron Mine'', Dingwall, 1990 {{ISBN|0951487000}}.
* {{en}} John Nicholson - ''I Remember: Memories Of Raasay'', Birlinn, Edinburgh, 2002.
* {{en}} Prunella Stack - ''Island Quest. The Inner Hebrides'', Collins/Harvill Press, London, 1979 {{ISBN|0002623234}}.
* {{en}} N. Morton et J. D. Hudson - ''Field guide to the Jurassic of the Isles of Raasay and Skye, Inner Hebrides, NW Scotland'' dans Field guide to the British Jurassic, P. D. Taylor éditeur, Geological Society, London, 1995.

